    "Here we only consider rotational noise since it has more pronounced effect on particle trajectories than linear velocity noise 87.",
    "The mobility α and force F embody the interaction between the particle and the obstacles.",
    "Note that the vertical collisions between the CAP and the substrate give rise to an effective active Brownian motion like behavior for the CAP in the horizontal plane, the inertial effect is accounted for by the model parameters v 0, ω 0, and D r.",
